{"tid":2435073,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"徐麗泰：民主派無資格被諮詢","createTime":"2021-03-06T03:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T03:35:34.000Z","uid":290118,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"40a6e37a7104eb66513835ffd518022f685697a9","tid":2435073,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T03:27:43.000Z","msg":"XG01 <br />\n<br />\n全國人大會議昨日（5日）開幕，將審議《全國人民代表大會關於完善香港特別行政區選舉制度的決定（草案）》，出手重劃特首選委會及立法會兩個選舉辦法。對於有輿論指中央今次出手，未有經過香港各界廣泛諮詢，前全國人大常委范徐麗泰稱香港的政制發展不是香港「話事」，事權在於人大。<br />\n<br />\n對於今次完善選舉制度不是由香港主動提出，范徐麗泰稱是因為時間上根本做不到、來不及，實際操作上也有困難。她承認，沒有諮詢每一位香港人是事實，但亦有很多香港人曾提出意見。至於為何只諮詢建制派而沒有民主派，范徐麗泰反問反對派有多少不是亂港分子、沒有勾結外國勢力、傷害香港繁榮穩定，直指這些人「根本上已經沒有了被諮詢的資格」。"},{"pid":"6b6b0f9d247fd834afa7ad7589851d5de0465f01","tid":2435073,"uid":82640,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T03:28:24.000Z","msg":"連人人平等都否定嘅社會主義國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a80f942182a82431c21ef2341adfb90c05946b","tid":2435073,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b6b0f9d247fd834afa7ad7589851d5de0465f01","tid":2435073,"uid":82640,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T03:28:24.000Z","msg":"連人人平等都否定嘅社會主義國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T03:30:01.000Z","msg":"唔愛国無資格講平等<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbfe8935cb9faaf5728916f6ed6e91b272cd10f","tid":2435073,"uid":95577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"剝奪政治權利終身？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483185c41f30a9d7b534a5a35dce0549425e428d","tid":2435073,"uid":362366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T03:31:47.000Z","msg":"証明一國兩制徹底失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩制之中獨裁制完全踐踏民主制"},{"pid":"ad41fcb79265dc336ea7a998905f37bae5f192af","tid":2435073,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T03:33:23.000Z","msg":"太聲啲講一國兩制名存實亡咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff46dd2cc175a78e6520f93201856a40366e112e","tid":2435073,"uid":362015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T03:33:36.000Z","msg":"自己玩飽佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c2e21f697f23c193317604de5cfd690b855026","tid":2435073,"uid":173356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T03:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}